data.description: You must see this charming home that is completely move-in ready! You will love the layout of each space, designed to maximize every last square foot of space. The pristine, premium flooring is a huge compliment to the homes charm and style. The kitchen is the perfect size for everyday meal preparation while still part of the flow of the home, it is also just tucked away enough to have some separation if needed. Please note, the photos have been virtually staged.
